Frequently Asked Questions

How do I list an item for rent?

Create an account, go to your dashboard, and click "Post Listings". Fill in the details and upload photos.

What are the rental periods available?

We offer daily and monthly rental options. Choose the period that best fits your needs.

How do I contact a renter?

Use our messaging system to communicate directly with renters. All conversations are saved in your dashboard.

Is there a fee for listing items?

Basic listings are free. Premium features and advertising options are available for a small fee.

How do I report a problem with a listing?

Use the "Report" button on any listing or contact our support team directly.

Can I edit my listing after posting?

Yes, go to your dashboard, find the listing under "My Listings", and click "Edit".
